{"assertion_id": "assert-00001", "assertion_type": "person_action", "subject": {"entity_id": "person-0001", "label": "郭畀"}, "predicate": "traveled_to", "object": {"entity_id": "place-0002", "value": "錢塘", "value_type": "entity"}, "qualifiers": {}, "source_entry_ids": ["entry-0019"], "source_action": null, "evidence_raw": "十六日，晴。送所寫《遺教經》還甘露長老。晚趁呂城夜航，作錢塘之行。", "evidence_translation_ko": null, "certainty": "confirmed", "certainty_reason": null, "negated": false, "provenance": {"generated_by": "scripts/phase_d_pipeline.py", "generated_at": "2026-03-29T11:17:47+09:00", "source_annotation_review": "reviewed"}}
{"assertion_id": "assert-00002", "assertion_type": "person_action", "subject": {"entity_id": "person-0001", "label": "郭畀"}, "predicate": "visited", "object": {"entity_id": "person-0003", "value": "白湛淵", "value_type": "entity"}, "qualifiers": {"result": "not_met"}, "source_entry_ids": ["entry-0020"], "source_action": null, "evidence_raw": "十七日，午前抵呂城壩下，倒換小舟，至奔牛復換小舟。晡時至常州，入城，元豐橋見白湛淵提舉，値岀江陰未囘。乃子无咎、次子无華留歇。同白无咎到太平寺，觀壁上畫水中作一筆繞之不斷，立視久之，若洶湧生動之意，奇筆也。寺僧具茶，茶已乃出，門外建新塔方成。晚，二白兄具酒晚飯，宿于无華書院。", "evidence_translation_ko": null, "certainty": "uncertain", "certainty_reason": "review notes mark the visit as unsuccessful", "negated": true, "provenance": {"generated_by": "scripts/phase_d_pipeline.py", "generated_at": "2026-03-29T11:17:47+09:00", "source_annotation_review": "reviewed"}}
{"assertion_id": "assert-00003", "assertion_type": "person_action", "subject": {"entity_id": "person-0001", "label": "郭畀"}, "predicate": "visited", "object": {"entity_id": "person-0008", "value": "蔡德甫", "value_type": "entity"}, "qualifiers": {}, "source_entry_ids": ["entry-0021"], "source_action": null, "evidence_raw": "十八日，晴。早尋蔡德甫來說話，无咎待早飯，蔡兄同。无咎借馬同岀訪馬習齋教授于郡學，會龜山王山長、劉練江、馬教，仍約午集。同无咎囘，蔡德甫禮留小酌，煮蟹蒸芋。次訪李仲謙。出門，解后包古江山長。赴馬習齋之約，坐客羅漢臣、余及白无咎，食五品酒，散作别。次别无咎昆仲，登夜航之姑蘇。有北客喧呼，至二更乃睡。", "evidence_translation_ko": null, "certainty": "confirmed", "certainty_reason": null, "negated": false, "provenance": {"generated_by": "scripts/phase_d_pipeline.py", "generated_at": "2026-03-29T11:17:47+09:00", "source_annotation_review": "reviewed"}}
{"assertion_id": "assert-00004", "assertion_type": "person_action", "subject": {"entity_id": "person-0001", "label": "郭畀"}, "predicate": "dined_with", "object": {"entity_id": "person-0009", "value": "白无咎", "value_type": "entity"}, "qualifiers": {}, "source_entry_ids": ["entry-0021"], "source_action": null, "evidence_raw": "十八日，晴。早尋蔡德甫來說話，无咎待早飯，蔡兄同。无咎借馬同岀訪馬習齋教授于郡學，會龜山王山長、劉練江、馬教，仍約午集。同无咎囘，蔡德甫禮留小酌，煮蟹蒸芋。次訪李仲謙。出門，解后包古江山長。赴馬習齋之約，坐客羅漢臣、余及白无咎，食五品酒，散作别。次别无咎昆仲，登夜航之姑蘇。有北客喧呼，至二更乃睡。", "evidence_translation_ko": null, "certainty": "confirmed", "certainty_reason": null, "negated": false, "provenance": {"generated_by": "scripts/phase_d_pipeline.py", "generated_at": "2026-03-29T11:17:47+09:00", "source_annotation_review": "reviewed"}}
{"assertion_id": "assert-00005", "assertion_type": "person_action", "subject": {"entity_id": "person-0001", "label": "郭畀"}, "predicate": "visited", "object": {"entity_id": "person-0016", "value": "龔子敬", "value_type": "entity"}, "qualifiers": {}, "source_entry_ids": ["entry-0022"], "source_action": null, "evidence_raw": "十九日，午後抵平江，見龔子敬山長，父子留宿，具晚飯。飯已，留燈夜語，是夜多蚊。", "evidence_translation_ko": null, "certainty": "confirmed", "certainty_reason": null, "negated": false, "provenance": {"generated_by": "scripts/phase_d_pipeline.py", "generated_at": "2026-03-29T11:17:47+09:00", "source_annotation_review": "reviewed"}}
