{"assertion_id": "assert-00011", "assertion_type": "person_action", "subject": {"entity_id": "person-0001", "label": "郭畀"}, "predicate": "visited", "object": {"entity_id": "person-0045", "value": "趙子昂", "value_type": "entity"}, "qualifiers": {"result": "not_met"}, "source_entry_ids": ["entry-0027"], "source_action": null, "evidence_raw": "二十四日，晴，客杭。早到省中照磨所，見李叔義，改抹元文。到儒學提舉司，攜李兄書，見王一初都目，投呈子，會王夀之、王子芳、任伯和。是日，分付該吏金君玉承行。次約金君玉、毛令史市樓小集。雨作。湖上兜率寺，見趙子昂學士不遇，乃姪趙仲美具茶訖，致意。是日遇牟學甫、宗夀卿、徐君美、袁義甫、楊廷秀、丹徒宣差狄仁卿、田君美、蔡宣使、許芳所應旂。", "evidence_translation_ko": null, "certainty": "uncertain", "certainty_reason": "review notes mark the attempt as unsuccessful", "negated": true, "provenance": {"generated_by": "scripts/phase_d_pipeline.py", "generated_at": "2026-03-29T11:17:47+09:00", "source_annotation_review": "reviewed"}}
{"assertion_id": "assert-00012", "assertion_type": "person_action", "subject": {"entity_id": "person-0001", "label": "郭畀"}, "predicate": "visited", "object": {"entity_id": "person-0026", "value": "李叔義", "value_type": "entity"}, "qualifiers": {}, "source_entry_ids": ["entry-0028"], "source_action": null, "evidence_raw": "二十五日，陰，客杭。早到省中見李叔義。次入禮房，見張德輝外郞，話乃事。到提舉司，催金君玉書卷，王一初未允。再到省中，見李叔義，託見王公。范成之主簿來。晚，張德輝請說話，會丘中山教授。德輝檢尋解由未見，託爲挨問。見范成之。尹子源約小飮。是夜，客樓暄甚，必雨作也。", "evidence_translation_ko": null, "certainty": "confirmed", "certainty_reason": null, "negated": false, "provenance": {"generated_by": "scripts/phase_d_pipeline.py", "generated_at": "2026-03-29T11:17:47+09:00", "source_annotation_review": "reviewed"}}
