{"assertion_id": "assert-00020", "assertion_type": "person_action", "subject": {"entity_id": "person-0001", "label": "郭畀"}, "predicate": "visited", "object": {"entity_id": "person-0002", "value": "甘露長老", "value_type": "entity"}, "qualifiers": {}, "source_entry_ids": ["entry-0019"], "source_action": null, "evidence_raw": "十六日，晴。送所寫《遺教經》還甘露長老。晚趁呂城夜航，作錢塘之行。", "evidence_translation_ko": null, "certainty": "confirmed", "certainty_reason": "감로 장로", "negated": false, "provenance": {"generated_by": "scripts/phase_d_pipeline.py", "generated_at": "2026-03-29T11:17:47+09:00", "source_annotation_review": "reviewed"}}
{"assertion_id": "assert-00021", "assertion_type": "person_action", "subject": {"entity_id": "person-0001", "label": "郭畀"}, "predicate": "traveled_to", "object": {"entity_id": "place-0008", "value": "无華書院", "value_type": "entity"}, "qualifiers": {}, "source_entry_ids": ["entry-0020"], "source_action": null, "evidence_raw": "十七日，午前抵呂城壩下，倒換小舟，至奔牛復換小舟。晡時至常州，入城，元豐橋見白湛淵提舉，値岀江陰未囘。乃子无咎、次子无華留歇。同白无咎到太平寺，觀壁上畫水中作一筆繞之不斷，立視久之，若洶湧生動之意，奇筆也。寺僧具茶，茶已乃出，門外建新塔方成。晚，二白兄具酒晚飯，宿于无華書院。", "evidence_translation_ko": null, "certainty": "confirmed", "certainty_reason": null, "negated": false, "provenance": {"generated_by": "scripts/phase_d_pipeline.py", "generated_at": "2026-03-29T11:17:47+09:00", "source_annotation_review": "reviewed"}}
